name: move_three_objects_seed42
description: The robot should move each of the three 0.5m cubed blocks from their start location onto the platform by pushing them individually.

children.name: walk_to_cube_for_robot_to_push_1
children.description: The robot should walk to a position near the first 'Cube for robot to push' (Object1) to prepare for pushing. The goal state is for the robot to be positioned appropriately to initiate a push on 'Cube for robot to push' (Object1).

children.name: push_cube_for_robot_to_push_1_towards_platform_for_cubes
children.description: The robot should push the first 'Cube for robot to push' (Object1) in the general direction of 'Platform for cubes' (Object4). The goal state is for 'Cube for robot to push' (Object1) to be significantly displaced from its starting position and moving towards or near 'Platform for cubes' (Object4).

children.name: push_cube_for_robot_to_push_1_onto_platform_for_cubes
children.description: The robot should perform final pushes on the first 'Cube for robot to push' (Object1) to ensure it is fully and stably positioned on 'Platform for cubes' (Object4). The goal state is for 'Cube for robot to push' (Object1) to be entirely on 'Platform for cubes' (Object4) and stable.
